<CDLItem itemNbr="33-41-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.CDL.3-33-41-01.1.3-33-41-01">
<Title>Wing Illumination Light Lens</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Any number may be missing. For each missing light lens, open the appropriate circuit breaker using a flight deck multi-function display and lock with an INOP tag. Cover the light assembly opening with speed tape. Inspect speed tape every other flight. The associated wing illumination light must be considered inoperative.</Para>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must be dispatched using MEL item 33-41-01.</Para>
</Note>
